### Packages API Tests

### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### 1. Get All Group Packages
GET {{baseUrl}}/package/group-packages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Create New Group Package (Owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/package/group-packages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1,
    "title": "Premium Group Package",
    "description": "A premium package for group training"
}

### 3. Get Group Package Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/package/group-packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Update Group Package
PUT {{baseUrl}}/package/group-packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "gym": 1,
    "title": "Updated Group Package",
    "description": "Updated description"
}

### 5. Delete Group Package
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/package/group-packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Get All Packages
GET {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 7. Create New Package (Owner only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "group_package": 1,
    "title": "Male Monthly Package",
    "description": "Monthly package for male members",
    "gender": "male",
    "price": 500000.00,
    "duration": 30,
    "commission_rate": 0.05
}

### 8. Get Package Details
GET {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Update Package
PUT {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "group_package": 1,
    "title": "Updated Package",
    "description": "Updated description",
    "gender": "female",
    "price": 600000.00,
    "duration": 30,
    "commission_rate": 0.05
}

### 10. Partial Update Package
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "price": 550000.00
}

### 11. Delete Package
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/package/packages/1/
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
